---
description: Design System with screens, nodes, and interaction flows.
alwaysApply: false
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Insight Canvas — Design Spec</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #eeeef5;
    --bg2: #f0f0f8;
    --surface: #ffffff;
    --surface2: #f7f7fc;
    --surface3: #f0f0f8;
    --border: #e2e2ee;
    --border-bright: #d4d4e8;
    --text: #0f0f1a;
    --text-muted: #6b6b8a;
    --text-dim: #a0a0bc;

    --chart: #3b82f6;
    --chart-bg: #eff6ff;
    --chart-border: #bfdbfe;

    --insight: #059669;
    --insight-bg: #ecfdf5;
    --insight-border: #a7f3d0;

    --hypothesis: #d97706;
    --hypothesis-bg: #fffbeb;
    --hypothesis-border: #fde68a;

    --experiment: #dc2626;
    --experiment-bg: #fef2f2;
    --experiment-border: #fecaca;

    --action: #7c3aed;
    --action-bg: #f5f3ff;
    --action-border: #ddd6fe;

    --question: #db2777;
    --question-bg: #fdf2f8;
    --question-border: #fbcfe8;

    --accent: #6366f1;
    --accent-light: #eef2ff;
    --accent-border: #c7d2fe;

    --grad-text: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #06b6d4 100%);

}

- { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
background: var(--bg);
color: var(--text);
font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
font-weight: 400;
line-height: 1.6;
padding: 56px 48px;
max-width: 1360px;
margin: 0 auto;
position: relative;
}

body::before {
content: '';
position: fixed;
inset: 0;
background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #9999cc18 1px, transparent 1px);
background-size: 24px 24px;
pointer-events: none;
z-index: 0;
}

body > \* { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

.doc-header {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
gap: 16px;
margin-bottom: 72px;
padding-bottom: 48px;
border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
}
.doc-eyebrow {
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 8px;
background: var(--surface);
border: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
border-radius: 100px;
padding: 5px 14px;
width: fit-content;
box-shadow: 0 1px 3px #00000008;
}
.eyebrow-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--insight); }
.eyebrow-label { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.01em; }
.doc-title {
font-size: 52px;
font-weight: 800;
line-height: 1.05;
letter-spacing: -0.04em;
color: var(--text);
}
.doc-title span {
background: var(--grad-text);
-webkit-background-clip: text;
-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
background-clip: text;
}
.doc-subtitle { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; max-width: 540px; line-height: 1.7; }
.doc-meta {
display: flex;
border: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
border-radius: 8px;
overflow: hidden;
width: fit-content;
background: var(--surface);
box-shadow: 0 1px 3px #00000008;
}
.doc-meta span {
font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
font-size: 10px;
color: var(--text-dim);
padding: 6px 14px;
border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}
.doc-meta span:last-child { border-right: none; }

.section { margin-bottom: 88px; }
.section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.section-num {
font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
font-size: 10px;
color: var(--text-dim);
background: var(--surface);
border: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
border-radius: 4px;
padding: 2px 7px;
letter-spacing: 0.06em;
}
.section-title { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--text); }
.section-rule { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border-bright); }

.screen-frame {
border: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
border-radius: 16px;
overflow: hidden;
background: var(--surface);
margin-bottom: 28px;
box-shadow: 0 4px 24px #00000010, 0 1px 4px #00000008;
}
.screen-chrome {
background: var(--surface2);
border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
padding: 10px 16px;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 8px;
}
.chrome-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
.chrome-dot.r { background: #ff5f57; }
.chrome-dot.y { background: #febc2e; }
.chrome-dot.g { background: #28c840; }
.chrome-url {
margin-left: 8px;
flex: 1;
background: var(--surface);
border: 1px solid var(--border);
border-radius: 5px;
padding: 3px 10px;
font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
font-size: 10px;
color: var(--text-dim);
}
.screen-name { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }

.app-shell { display: flex; height: 620px; }

.sidebar {
width: 210px;
background: var(--surface2);
border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
flex-shrink: 0;
}
.sidebar-logo { padding: 16px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); }
.logo-icon { width: 22px; height: 22px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #06b6d4); border-radius: 6px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.sidebar-section { padding: 14px 14px 4px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
.sidebar-item { margin: 1px 8px; padding: 7px 10px; border-radius: 7px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.sidebar-item.active { background: var(--accent-light); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--accent-border); font-weight: 500; }
.sidebar-item .dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--insight); flex-shrink: 0; }
.sidebar-item .dot.y { background: var(--hypothesis); }
.sidebar-item .dot.p { background: var(--action); }
.sidebar-bottom { margin-top: auto; padding: 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
.btn-new { width: 100%; padding: 7px; background: var(--text); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 7px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; }

.canvas-area {
flex: 1;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
background:
radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 30%, #6366f10c 0%, transparent 50%),
radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 70%, #06b6d40a 0%, transparent 50%),
repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 31px, #6b6b8a08 31px, #6b6b8a08 32px),
repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 31px, #6b6b8a08 31px, #6b6b8a08 32px);
background-color: #f4f4fb;
}
.canvas-toolbar {
position: absolute; top: 14px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-bright); border-radius: 8px;
padding: 4px; display: flex; gap: 2px; z-index: 10; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #00000010;
}
.tb-btn { padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted); border: none; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; }
.tb-btn.active { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.tb-btn.accent { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
.canvas-zoom {
position: absolute; bottom: 14px; right: 14px;
background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-bright); border-radius: 7px;
display: flex; overflow: hidden; z-index: 10; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px #00000008;
}
.zoom-btn { padding: 5px 9px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); border: none; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
.zoom-btn:last-child { border-right: none; }
.zoom-pct { padding: 5px 9px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-dim); }
.canvas-svg { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; pointer-events: none; }

.node {
position: absolute; border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px;
border: 1px solid; width: 192px; background: white;
box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #00000010;
}
.node-type { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; }
.node-type::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: currentColor; flex-shrink: 0; }
.node-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.35; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: var(--text); }
.node-body { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
.node-footer { margin-top: 8px; padding-top: 7px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); }
.node.chart { border-color: var(--chart-border); }
.node.insight { border-color: var(--insight-border); }
.node.hypo { border-color: var(--hypothesis-border); }
.node.exp { border-color: var(--experiment-border); }
.node.chart .node-type { color: var(--chart); }
.node.insight .node-type { color: var(--insight); }
.node.hypo .node-type { color: var(--hypothesis); }
.node.exp .node-type { color: var(--experiment); }

.chart-bars { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 3px; height: 28px; margin-top: 6px; }
.bar { flex: 1; background: var(--chart); border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0; opacity: 0.55; }

.chat-panel { width: 268px; background: var(--surface); border-left: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-shrink: 0; }
.chat-header { padding: 12px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; color: var(--text); }
.chat-status { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--insight); }
.status-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--insight); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
@keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0.3} }
.chat-messages { flex: 1; padding: 12px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
.msg { max-width: 85%; padding: 8px 11px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.5; }
.msg.user { align-self: flex-end; background: var(--accent); color: white; border-radius: 10px 10px 2px 10px; }
.msg.agent { align-self: flex-start; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-muted); border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 2px; }
.msg-action { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--insight); margin-top: 5px; padding: 3px 7px; background: var(--insight-bg); border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--insight-border); }
.chat-input { padding: 10px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
.input-box { background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 7px 10px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
.send-btn { width: 22px; height: 22px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 5px; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 11px; color: white; font-weight: 700; }

.annotations { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-top: 18px; }
.annotation { display: flex; gap: 10px; padding: 14px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px #00000006; }
.ann-num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-light); border: 1px solid var(--accent-border); border-radius: 5px; width: 22px; height: 22px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
.ann-content h4 { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 3px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: var(--text); }
.ann-content p { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55; }

.node-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.node-card { background: var(--surface); border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px; border: 1px solid var(--border); box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #00000008; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.node-card::after { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; }
.node-card.chart::after { background: var(--chart); }
.node-card.insight::after { background: var(--insight); }
.node-card.hypo::after { background: var(--hypothesis); }
.node-card.exp::after { background: var(--experiment); }
.node-card.action::after { background: var(--action); }
.node-card.question::after{ background: var(--question); }
.nc-label { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.nc-label.chart { color: var(--chart); }
.nc-label.insight { color: var(--insight); }
.nc-label.hypo { color: var(--hypothesis); }
.nc-label.exp { color: var(--experiment); }
.nc-label.action { color: var(--action); }
.nc-label.question{ color: var(--question); }
.nc-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
.nc-dot.chart { background: var(--chart); }
.nc-dot.insight { background: var(--insight); }
.nc-dot.hypo { background: var(--hypothesis); }
.nc-dot.exp { background: var(--experiment); }
.nc-dot.action { background: var(--action); }
.nc-dot.question{ background: var(--question); }
.nc-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); }
.nc-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.nc-example { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic; background: var(--surface2); padding: 6px 8px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }

.palette-strip { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px #00000008; }
.palette-label { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
.swatch-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.swatch { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; align-items: center; }
.swatch-color { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
.swatch-name { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 8px; color: var(--text-dim); text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; }

.flow-diagram { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 22px 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #00000008; }
.flow-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); }
.flow-badge { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 100px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; font-weight: 500; }
.flow-badge.f1 { background: var(--insight-bg); color: var(--insight); border: 1px solid var(--insight-border); }
.flow-badge.f2 { background: var(--hypothesis-bg); color: var(--hypothesis); border: 1px solid var(--hypothesis-border); }
.flow-badge.f3 { background: var(--chart-bg); color: var(--chart); border: 1px solid var(--chart-border); }
.flow-badge.f4 { background: var(--action-bg); color: var(--action); border: 1px solid var(--action-border); }
.flow-steps { display: flex; align-items: stretch; overflow-x: auto; }
.flow-step { min-width: 130px; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
.step-box { width: 100%; padding: 11px 10px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid; text-align: center; }
.step-actor { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.step-actor.user { color: var(--accent); }
.step-actor.agent { color: var(--insight); }
.step-actor.canvas { color: var(--chart); }
.step-actor.output { color: var(--action); }
.step-action { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 3px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
.step-detail { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.4; }
.step-box.user-box { background: var(--accent-light); border-color: var(--accent-border); }
.step-box.agent-box { background: var(--insight-bg); border-color: var(--insight-border); }
.step-box.result-box { background: var(--chart-bg); border-color: var(--chart-border); }
.step-box.system-box { background: var(--action-bg); border-color: var(--action-border); }
.step-arrow { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 5px; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 22px; }
.arrow-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border-bright); position: relative; }
.arrow-line::after { content: '▶'; position: absolute; right: -5px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); font-size: 7px; color: var(--text-dim); }
.flow-notes { margin-top: 12px; display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.flow-note { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-muted); padding: 3px 9px; background: var(--surface2); border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
.flow-note strong { color: var(--text); }

.drawer-overlay { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15); z-index: 20; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; }
.drawer { width: 310px; background: var(--surface); border-left: 1px solid var(--border); height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: -4px 0 24px #00000014; }
.drawer-header { padding: 18px 18px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.drawer-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 3px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); }
.drawer-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
.drawer-body { flex: 1; padding: 16px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; overflow: auto; }
.upload-zone { border: 1.5px dashed var(--border-bright); border-radius: 10px; padding: 22px; text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 5px; background: var(--surface2); }
.upload-icon { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.upload-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
.upload-sub { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
.upload-btn { margin-top: 6px; padding: 5px 14px; background: var(--text); color: white; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
.drawer-label { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
.dataset-item { padding: 10px 12px; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; cursor: pointer; }
.dataset-item.selected { border-color: var(--accent-border); background: var(--accent-light); }
.dataset-icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.dataset-icon.green { background: var(--insight-bg); border: 1px solid var(--insight-border); }
.dataset-icon.blue { background: var(--chart-bg); border: 1px solid var(--chart-border); }
.dataset-info { flex: 1; }
.dataset-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 2px; color: var(--text); }
.dataset-meta { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); }
.check { width: 15px; height: 15px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 8px; color: white; font-weight: 800; }

.detail-panel { width: 292px; background: var(--surface); border-left: 1px solid var(--border); height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.detail-header { padding: 14px 14px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.detail-node-type { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 5px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; }
.detail-node-type.insight { color: var(--insight); }
.detail-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.35; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); }
.detail-body { flex: 1; padding: 14px; overflow: auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
.detail-section-title { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 5px; }
.detail-text { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
.evidence-item { padding: 6px 9px; background: var(--insight-bg); border-radius: 5px; border-left: 2px solid var(--insight); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 3px; }
.editable-field { background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 7px; padding: 9px 10px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.5; position: relative; }
.field-edit-icon { position: absolute; top: 7px; right: 8px; font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-dim); }
.connected-nodes { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; }
.connected-node { padding: 5px 9px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
.connected-node.chart { background: var(--chart-bg); color: var(--chart); border: 1px solid var(--chart-border); }
.connected-node.hypo { background: var(--hypothesis-bg); color: var(--hypothesis); border: 1px solid var(--hypothesis-border); }
.detail-footer { padding: 10px 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; gap: 6px; }
.detail-btn { flex: 1; padding: 7px; border-radius: 7px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; }
.detail-btn.primary { background: var(--text); color: white; }
.detail-btn.secondary { background: var(--surface2); color: var(--text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); font-weight: 500; }

.history-content { flex: 1; padding: 18px; overflow: auto; background: var(--bg); }
.history-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
.session-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 14px; cursor: pointer; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px #00000008; }
.session-date { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 5px; }
.session-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text); }
.session-nodes { display: flex; gap: 4px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.session-node-badge { padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 100px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; font-weight: 500; }
.session-node-badge.chart { background: var(--chart-bg); color: var(--chart); border: 1px solid var(--chart-border); }
.session-node-badge.insight { background: var(--insight-bg); color: var(--insight); border: 1px solid var(--insight-border); }
.session-node-badge.hypo { background: var(--hypothesis-bg); color: var(--hypothesis); border: 1px solid var(--hypothesis-border); }
.session-node-badge.exp { background: var(--experiment-bg); color: var(--experiment); border: 1px solid var(--experiment-border); }
.session-footer { margin-top: 8px; padding-top: 7px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
.memory-banner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-light), #ecfdf5); border: 1px solid var(--accent-border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; }
.memory-icon { font-size: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.memory-text { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.55; }
.memory-text strong { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

.trace-panel { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 1px 4px #00000008; }
.trace-header { padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; background: var(--surface2); }
.trace-toggle { color: var(--accent); cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; }
.trace-item { padding: 7px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; }
.trace-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.trace-time { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-dim); flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 1px; }
.trace-content { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }
.trace-tag { display: inline; font-size: 8px; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; margin-right: 5px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; font-weight: 600; }
.trace-tag.tool { background: var(--chart-bg); color: var(--chart); border: 1px solid var(--chart-border); }
.trace-tag.node { background: var(--insight-bg); color: var(--insight); border: 1px solid var(--insight-border); }
.trace-tag.think { background: var(--hypothesis-bg); color: var(--hypothesis); border: 1px solid var(--hypothesis-border); }

.script-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
.script-beat { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #00000008; }
.beat-time { padding: 7px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-light); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
.beat-body { padding: 14px; }
.beat-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--text); }
.beat-steps { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
.beat-steps li { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); padding-left: 14px; position: relative; line-height: 1.4; }
.beat-steps li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--text-dim); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; }
.beat-highlight { margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px 10px; background: var(--surface2); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); border-left: 2px solid var(--accent-border); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5; }

.mt-24 { margin-top: 24px; }
</style>

</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="doc-header">
  <div class="doc-eyebrow">
    <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
    <span class="eyebrow-label">Design Spec · v1.0 · CopilotKit + React Flow</span>
  </div>
  <h1 class="doc-title">Insight Canvas<br><span>Design System</span></h1>
  <p class="doc-subtitle">Screens, nodes, and interaction flows for the collaborative AI reasoning demo app. Built on CopilotKit A2-UI and React Flow.</p>
  <div class="doc-meta">
    <span>4 SCREENS</span>
    <span>6 NODE TYPES</span>
    <span>4 FLOWS</span>
    <span>3-MIN SCRIPT</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 01 — NODE TYPES -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">01</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Node Types</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="node-grid">
    <div class="node-card chart">
      <div class="nc-label chart"><span class="nc-dot chart"></span>Chart</div>
      <div class="nc-title">Chart</div>
      <div class="nc-desc">Visualization generated by the AI agent via MCP App. Can be line, bar, or scatter chart.</div>
      <div class="nc-example">"Churn rate evolution by week of life"</div>
    </div>
    <div class="node-card insight">
      <div class="nc-label insight"><span class="nc-dot insight"></span>Insight</div>
      <div class="nc-title">Insight</div>
      <div class="nc-desc">Data-driven observation derived from the chart or dataset. Concrete claim with supporting evidence.</div>
      <div class="nc-example">"Churn spikes 40% for users with less than 7 active days"</div>
    </div>
    <div class="node-card hypo">
      <div class="nc-label hypo"><span class="nc-dot hypo"></span>Hypothesis</div>
      <div class="nc-title">Hypothesis</div>
      <div class="nc-desc">Possible explanation for an insight. Can be edited by the user or generated by the agent.</div>
      <div class="nc-example">"Onboarding doesn't show product value before day 7"</div>
    </div>
    <div class="node-card exp">
      <div class="nc-label exp"><span class="nc-dot exp"></span>Experiment</div>
      <div class="nc-title">Experiment</div>
      <div class="nc-desc">Test plan to validate the hypothesis. Includes success metrics and cutoff criteria.</div>
      <div class="nc-example">"A/B test: interactive tutorial days 1–3. Goal: –15% churn in 30 days"</div>
    </div>
    <div class="node-card action">
      <div class="nc-label action"><span class="nc-dot action"></span>Action Item</div>
      <div class="nc-title">Action Item</div>
      <div class="nc-desc">Concrete operational task derived from the analysis. Has an owner and estimated date.</div>
      <div class="nc-example">"Redesign onboarding screen — product team, sprint 24"</div>
    </div>
    <div class="node-card question">
      <div class="nc-label question"><span class="nc-dot question"></span>Question</div>
      <div class="nc-title">Question</div>
      <div class="nc-desc">Open investigation point without an answer yet. Generates new branches on the canvas.</div>
      <div class="nc-example">"Is there a churn difference between mobile and desktop in week 1?"</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="palette-strip">
    <span class="palette-label">Color palette</span>
    <div class="swatch-row">
      <div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#3b82f6;"></div><div class="swatch-name">Chart<br>#3b82f6</div></div>
      <div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#059669;"></div><div class="swatch-name">Insight<br>#059669</div></div>
      <div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#d97706;"></div><div class="swatch-name">Hypothesis<br>#d97706</div></div>
      <div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#dc2626;"></div><div class="swatch-name">Experiment<br>#dc2626</div></div>
      <div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#7c3aed;"></div><div class="swatch-name">Action<br>#7c3aed</div></div>
      <div class="swatch"><div class="swatch-color" style="background:#db2777;"></div><div class="swatch-name">Question<br>#db2777</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 02 — MAIN CANVAS -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">02</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Primary Screen — Canvas</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="screen-frame">
    <div class="screen-chrome">
      <div class="chrome-dot r"></div><div class="chrome-dot y"></div><div class="chrome-dot g"></div>
      <div class="chrome-url">insight-canvas.app / session / churn-analysis-q4</div>
      <div class="screen-name">SCREEN 01 · MAIN CANVAS</div>
    </div>
    <div class="app-shell">
      <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-logo"><div class="logo-icon"></div>Insight Canvas</div>
        <div class="sidebar-section">Sessions</div>
        <div class="sidebar-item active"><span class="dot"></span>Churn Analysis Q4</div>
        <div class="sidebar-item"><span class="dot y"></span>Retention Deep Dive</div>
        <div class="sidebar-item"><span class="dot p"></span>Segmentation v2</div>
        <div class="sidebar-bottom"><div class="btn-new">+ New session</div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="canvas-area">
        <div class="canvas-toolbar">
          <button class="tb-btn active">Select</button>
          <button class="tb-btn">Move</button>
          <button class="tb-btn">Connect</button>
          <button class="tb-btn accent">Reasoning trace ↗</button>
        </div>
        <svg class="canvas-svg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <defs>
            <marker id="arr" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" refX="3" refY="3" orient="auto">
              <path d="M0,0 L0,6 L6,3 z" fill="#6b6b8a55"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>
          <line x1="290" y1="172" x2="372" y2="232" stroke="#6b6b8a28" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 3" marker-end="url(#arr)"/>
          <line x1="492" y1="258" x2="556" y2="296" stroke="#6b6b8a28" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 3" marker-end="url(#arr)"/>
          <line x1="688" y1="322" x2="742" y2="360" stroke="#6b6b8a28" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4 3" marker-end="url(#arr)"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="node chart" style="left:96px;top:92px;">
          <div class="node-type">Chart</div>
          <div class="node-title">Churn by week of life</div>
          <div class="chart-bars">
            <div class="bar" style="height:38%;"></div><div class="bar" style="height:52%;"></div>
            <div class="bar" style="height:88%;"></div><div class="bar" style="height:100%;"></div>
            <div class="bar" style="height:68%;"></div><div class="bar" style="height:48%;"></div>
            <div class="bar" style="height:32%;"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="node-footer">MCP App · users_2024.csv</div>
        </div>
        <div class="node insight" style="left:338px;top:180px;">
          <div class="node-type">Insight</div>
          <div class="node-title">Churn spike in week 3</div>
          <div class="node-body">40% of churned users leave before day 21. Consistent across Q4 cohorts.</div>
          <div class="node-footer">High confidence · 3 sources</div>
        </div>
        <div class="node hypo" style="left:520px;top:276px;">
          <div class="node-type">Hypothesis</div>
          <div class="node-title">Onboarding doesn't show value</div>
          <div class="node-body">Users don't reach the key feature before day 7.</div>
          <div class="node-footer">Edited by user · 14:32</div>
        </div>
        <div class="node exp" style="left:706px;top:342px;">
          <div class="node-type">Experiment</div>
          <div class="node-title">A/B: Interactive tutorial</div>
          <div class="node-body">Goal: –15% churn in 30d. Segment: new users.</div>
          <div class="node-footer">Generated by agent</div>
        </div>
        <div class="canvas-zoom">
          <button class="zoom-btn">−</button>
          <div class="zoom-pct">85%</div>
          <button class="zoom-btn">+</button>
          <button class="zoom-btn" style="font-size:9px;padding:5px 7px;">⊡</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chat-panel">
        <div class="chat-header">Agent <div class="chat-status"><div class="status-dot"></div>active</div></div>
        <div class="chat-messages">
          <div class="msg user">Identify churn risk patterns</div>
          <div class="msg agent">Analyzed the dataset. Found a churn concentration between days 14–21.<div class="msg-action">→ Generated: Chart + Insight + Hypothesis</div></div>
          <div class="msg user">I edited the hypothesis — seems like it's the onboarding</div>
          <div class="msg agent">Makes sense. Generated an experiment to validate with A/B test.<div class="msg-action">→ Added: Experiment node</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-input"><div class="input-box"><span>Type a prompt...</span><div class="send-btn">↑</div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="annotations">
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">1</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Sessions sidebar</h4><p>List of previous analyses. Active session is highlighted. "New session" button at the bottom.</p></div></div>
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">2</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Grid canvas</h4><p>Subtle lavender dot grid (matching CopilotKit aesthetic). Nodes are draggable and reconnectable. Free zoom with scroll.</p></div></div>
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">3</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Floating toolbar</h4><p>Canvas tools (select, move, connect). "Reasoning trace" button opens the traceability panel.</p></div></div>
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">4</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Chat side panel</h4><p>The agent shows what actions it took on the canvas ("→ Generated: Chart + Insight"). Input is always visible.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 03 — DATA SOURCES DRAWER -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">03</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Panel — Data Sources Drawer</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="screen-frame">
    <div class="screen-chrome">
      <div class="chrome-dot r"></div><div class="chrome-dot y"></div><div class="chrome-dot g"></div>
      <div class="chrome-url">insight-canvas.app / session / new</div>
      <div class="screen-name">SCREEN 02 · DATA DRAWER</div>
    </div>
    <div class="app-shell" style="position:relative;">
      <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-logo"><div class="logo-icon"></div>Insight Canvas</div>
        <div class="sidebar-section">Sessions</div>
        <div class="sidebar-item active"><span class="dot"></span>New session</div>
      </div>
      <div class="canvas-area" style="filter:blur(1px);opacity:0.5;">
        <div class="canvas-toolbar"><button class="tb-btn active">Select</button></div>
      </div>
      <div class="drawer-overlay">
        <div class="drawer">
          <div class="drawer-header">
            <div class="drawer-title">Data Sources</div>
            <div class="drawer-sub">Upload a file or choose a sample dataset to get started</div>
          </div>
          <div class="drawer-body">
            <div class="upload-zone">
              <div class="upload-icon">📂</div>
              <div class="upload-title">Drop your file here</div>
              <div class="upload-sub">CSV · XLSX · JSON · Max 50 MB</div>
              <div class="upload-btn">Browse file</div>
            </div>
            <div class="drawer-label">Sample datasets</div>
            <div class="dataset-item selected">
              <div class="dataset-icon green">📊</div>
              <div class="dataset-info"><div class="dataset-name">SaaS Churn Dataset</div><div class="dataset-meta">4.2K rows · 18 cols · users_2024.csv</div></div>
              <div class="check">✓</div>
            </div>
            <div class="dataset-item">
              <div class="dataset-icon blue">📈</div>
              <div class="dataset-info"><div class="dataset-name">E-commerce Retention</div><div class="dataset-meta">12K rows · 24 cols · retail_cohorts.csv</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="dataset-item">
              <div class="dataset-icon green">🏢</div>
              <div class="dataset-info"><div class="dataset-name">B2B Pipeline Analysis</div><div class="dataset-meta">890 rows · 31 cols · pipeline_q4.csv</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="annotations">
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">1</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Sliding drawer</h4><p>Slides in from the right. The canvas background stays visible but blurred, maintaining context.</p></div></div>
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">2</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Upload zone</h4><p>Drag & drop for CSV/XLSX/JSON. For the demo, pre-built datasets are used.</p></div></div>
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">3</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Sample datasets</h4><p>At least 2–3 pre-built datasets. Selected one shows a checkmark. One click activates it and closes the drawer.</p></div></div>
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">4</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Dataset metadata</h4><p>Row count, column count, and filename. Gives context before starting the analysis.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 04 — NODE DETAIL PANEL -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">04</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Panel — Node Detail</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="screen-frame">
    <div class="screen-chrome">
      <div class="chrome-dot r"></div><div class="chrome-dot y"></div><div class="chrome-dot g"></div>
      <div class="chrome-url">insight-canvas.app / session / churn-analysis-q4</div>
      <div class="screen-name">SCREEN 03 · NODE DETAIL</div>
    </div>
    <div class="app-shell">
