          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-footer">
          <div class="detail-btn secondary">Ask agent</div>
          <div class="detail-btn primary">Edit</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="annotations">
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">1</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Selected node ring</h4><p>The active node gets a 2px ring in its color. Other nodes fade slightly to give visual focus.</p></div></div>
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">2</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Supporting evidence</h4><p>Concrete data points backing the insight. Always generated by the agent, referenced to the dataset.</p></div></div>
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">3</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Free editable field</h4><p>Users can add notes to any node. Editing a hypothesis triggers the agent's response.</p></div></div>
    <div class="annotation"><div class="ann-num">4</div><div class="ann-content"><h4>Connected nodes</h4><p>Shows upstream (←) and downstream (→) nodes in the reasoning chain.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 05 — SESSION HISTORY -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">05</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Screen — Session History</h2>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="screen-frame">
    <div class="screen-chrome">
      <div class="chrome-dot r"></div><div class="chrome-dot y"></div><div class="chrome-dot g"></div>
      <div class="chrome-url">insight-canvas.app / sessions</div>
      <div class="screen-name">SCREEN 04 · SESSION HISTORY</div>
    </div>
    <div class="app-shell">
