          <li>Select "SaaS Churn Dataset"</li>
          <li>Drawer closes, active dataset appears in toolbar</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="beat-highlight">"We have a dataset of 4,000 SaaS users. Let's understand why they're churning."</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="script-beat">
      <div class="beat-time">0:30 – 1:30 · Generative Canvas</div>
      <div class="beat-body">
        <div class="beat-title">Agent generates the reasoning chain</div>
        <ul class="beat-steps">
          <li>Type prompt: "Identify churn risk patterns"</li>
          <li>Chart node appears with real visualization</li>
          <li>Insight node appears connected to chart</li>
          <li>Hypothesis node appears</li>
          <li>Open Reasoning Trace to show transparency</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="beat-highlight">"The agent doesn't just respond — it builds a visual reasoning map in real time."</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="script-beat">
      <div class="beat-time">1:30 – 2:15 · Co-Creation</div>
      <div class="beat-body">
        <div class="beat-title">User edits, agent responds</div>
        <ul class="beat-steps">
          <li>Click on the Hypothesis node</li>
          <li>Edit text: "specifically on day 3 of onboarding"</li>
          <li>Save → agent detects the change</li>
          <li>Experiment node appears with concrete plan</li>
          <li>Canvas expands automatically</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="beat-highlight">"I edit a hypothesis, the agent proposes how to test it. This is collaboration, not automation."</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="script-beat">
      <div class="beat-time">2:15 – 3:00 · Memory</div>
      <div class="beat-body">
        <div class="beat-title">Cross-session persistence</div>
        <ul class="beat-steps">
          <li>Navigate to the session history screen</li>
          <li>Show agent memory banner</li>
          <li>Open previous session → full canvas loads</li>
          <li>Agent proposes next investigation</li>
          <li>New branch is added to the canvas</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="beat-highlight">"This is structured, stateful collaboration between humans and agents."</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

